INSERT INTO infosec_processed VALUES(440,'CVE-2026-11455','A vulnerability was determined in FoundationAgents MetaGPT up to 0.8.2. Affected by this issue is the function check_cmd_exists of the file metagpt/utils/common.py. This manipulation of the argument mermaid.path causes command injection. The attack may be initiated remotely. A high degree of complexity is needed for the attack. The exploitation is known to be difficult. The exploit has been publicly disclosed and may be utilized. The project was informed of the problem early through an issue report but has not responded yet.','MetaGPT命令注入漏洞，可通过mermaid.path参数远程执行命令','漏洞',50,'FoundationAgents MetaGPT, metagpt/utils/common.py, check_cmd_exists函数','NVD','2026-06-07T09:16:20.403',NULL,NULL,1781418159,'https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln/detail/CVE-2026-11455');
INSERT INTO infosec_processed VALUES(441,'CVE-2026-11456','A vulnerability was identified in Chanjet CRM 1.0. This affects an unknown part of the file /tools/jxf_dump_systable.php of the component HTTP GET Request Handler. Such manipulation of the argument gblOrgID leads to sql injection. The attack may be launched remotely. The exploit is publicly available and might be used. The vendor was contacted early about this disclosure but did not respond in any way.','Chanjet CRM存在SQL注入漏洞，可通过gblOrgID参数远程利用','漏洞',73,'HTTP GET Request Handler','NVD','2026-06-07T09:16:21.673',NULL,NULL,1781418165,'https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln/detail/CVE-2026-11456');
INSERT INTO infosec_processed VALUES(442,'CVE-2026-11457','A security flaw has been discovered in erzhongxmu JeeWMS up to 141740afb2ba14d441c82a833d0a418d07ca2d69. This vulnerability affects unknown code of the file /base-boot/jmreport/testConnection of the component JimuReport test-connection Endpoint. Performing a manipulation of the argument dbType/dbDriver/dbUrl/dbUsername/dbPassword results in injection. Remote exploitation of the attack is possible. The exploit has been released to the public and may be used for attacks. This product follows a rolling release approach for continuous delivery, so version details for affected or updated releases are not provided. The vendor was contacted early about this disclosure but did not respond in any way.','JeeWMS JimuReport组件存在远程注入漏洞','漏洞',73,'JimuReport test-connection Endpoint','NVD','2026-06-07T09:16:21.843',NULL,NULL,1781418171,'https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln/detail/CVE-2026-11457');
INSERT INTO infosec_processed VALUES(443,'CVE-2026-11458','A weakness has been identified in erzhongxmu JeeWMS up to 141740afb2ba14d441c82a833d0a418d07ca2d69. This issue affects some unknown processing of the file /base-boot/actuator of the component Boot Actuator Endpoint. Executing a manipulation can lead to information disclosure. The attack can be executed remotely. The exploit has been made available to the public and could be used for attacks. This product implements a rolling release for ongoing delivery, which means version information for affected or updated releases is unavailable. The vendor was contacted early about this disclosure but did not respond in any way.','JeeWMS Boot Actuator组件存在远程信息泄露漏洞','漏洞',53,'Boot Actuator Endpoint','NVD','2026-06-07T09:16:22.050',NULL,NULL,1781418177,'https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln/detail/CVE-2026-11458');
INSERT INTO infosec_processed VALUES(444,'CVE-2026-11459','A security vulnerability has been detected in SecureAge CatchPulse up to 10.9.3. Impacted is an unknown function in the library saappctl.sys of the component IOCTL Handler. The manipulation leads to information disclosure. Local access is required to approach this attack. The exploit has been disclosed publicly and may be used.','SecureAge CatchPulse存在信息泄露漏洞','漏洞',33,'saappctl.sys','NVD','2026-06-07T10:16:21.863',NULL,NULL,1781418181,'https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln/detail/CVE-2026-11459');
INSERT INTO infosec_processed VALUES(445,'CVE-2026-49494','Comodo Internet Security''s firewall driver Inspect.sys contains an integer underflow in its IPv6 packet parser. The parser decrements an unsigned 64-bit payload-length value (taken from the IPv6 fixed header''s payload length field) by the size of each IPv6 extension header without validating it, so a packet whose declared payload length is smaller than the sum of its extension-header lengths underflows the value to a near-maximal 64-bit integer. Because IPv6 parsing occurs before firewall rule enforcement, a remote, unauthenticated attacker can send a single crafted IPv6 packet - even to a host with all ports blocked - to trigger an out-of-bounds read (and, on a separate code path, an oversized memcpy) in the Windows kernel at DISPATCH_LEVEL, crashing the system (BSOD).','Comodo防火墙IPv6解析整数下溢可致系统崩溃','漏洞',75,'Comodo Internet Security防火墙驱动Inspect.sys','NVD','2026-06-07T13:16:20.927',NULL,NULL,1781418189,'https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln/detail/CVE-2026-49494');
INSERT INTO infosec_processed VALUES(446,'CVE-2026-11460','A flaw has been found in Boost Serialization up to 1.91. The impacted element is an unknown function. This manipulation causes improper validation of specified type of input. It is possible to initiate the attack remotely. The exploit has been published and may be used. The maintainer was notified on Aug 2025 and a disclosure deadline was set for 90 days. The maintainer acknowledged but postponed indefinitely citing time concerns. No patch is currently available and the disclosure deadline has expired.','Boost Serialization库存在远程输入验证漏洞','漏洞',73,'Boost Serialization','NVD','2026-06-07T20:16:39.993',NULL,NULL,1781418194,'https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln/detail/CVE-2026-11460');
INSERT INTO infosec_processed VALUES(447,'CVE-2026-11461','A vulnerability has been found in NousResearch hermes-agent up to 0.12.0. This affects the function resolve_session_by_title of the file hermes_state.py of the component resume Endpoint. Such manipulation of the argument Title leads to authorization bypass. It is possible to launch the attack remotely. The exploit has been disclosed to the public and may be used. The vendor was contacted early about this disclosure but did not respond in any way.','hermes-agent授权绕过漏洞，可通过远程操作Title参数利用','漏洞',63,'hermes-agent resume endpoint','NVD','2026-06-07T22:16:22.547',NULL,NULL,1781418200,'https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln/detail/CVE-2026-11461');
INSERT INTO infosec_processed VALUES(448,'CVE-2026-11462','A vulnerability was found in Chengdu Everbrite Network Technology BeikeShop up to 1.6.0.22. This impacts the function callback of the file plugins/Stripe/Controllers/StripeController.php of the component Stripe Plugin. Performing a manipulation of the argument Request results in improper authorization. The attack can be initiated remotely. The exploit has been made public and could be used. The patch is named 6719e0fc690ea0a998452092862e0f0a17c65968. It is suggested to install a patch to address this issue.','BeikeShop插件不当授权漏洞，可通过远程请求参数操纵利用','漏洞',73,'Stripe Plugin','NVD','2026-06-07T23:16:41.040',NULL,NULL,1781418206,'https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln/detail/CVE-2026-11462');
INSERT INTO infosec_processed VALUES(449,'CVE-2026-11463','A vulnerability was determined in USCiLab Cereal up to 1.3.2. Affected is an unknown function of the component Shared Pointer Handler. Executing a manipulation can lead to type confusion. The attack can be launched remotely. The exploit has been publicly disclosed and may be utilized. The vendor was contacted early about this disclosure.','USCiLab Cereal共享指针处理器存在类型混淆漏洞','漏洞',73,'Shared Pointer Handler','NVD','2026-06-07T23:16:41.697',NULL,NULL,1781418212,'https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln/detail/CVE-2026-11463');
INSERT INTO infosec_processed VALUES(450,'CVE-2026-11464','A vulnerability was identified in JeecgBoot up to 3.9.2. Affected by this vulnerability is the function queryPageList of the file src\main\java\org\jeecg\modules\system\controller\SysUserController.java of the component User List Endpoint. The manipulation of the argument salt leads to information disclosure. The attack may be initiated remotely. The attack is considered to have high complexity. The exploitation appears to be difficult. The exploit is publicly available and might be used. A fix is planned for the upcoming release.','JeecgBoot用户列表接口存在信息泄露漏洞','漏洞',31,'User List Endpoint','NVD','2026-06-07T23:16:41.890',NULL,NULL,1781418222,'https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln/detail/CVE-2026-11464');
INSERT INTO infosec_processed VALUES(451,'CVE-2026-11465','A security flaw has been discovered in songquanpeng one-api up to 0.6.11-preview.7. Affected by this issue is the function Redeem of the file model/redemption.go of the component Redemption Code Top-Up Endpoint. The manipulation results in business logic errors. The attack may be launched remotely. The attack requires a high level of complexity. The exploitation is known to be difficult. The exploit has been released to the public and may be used for attacks. The pull request to fix this issue awaits acceptance.','one-api兑换码功能存在业务逻辑漏洞','漏洞',31,'Redemption Code Top-Up Endpoint','NVD','2026-06-07T23:16:42.060',NULL,NULL,1781418230,'https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln/detail/CVE-2026-11465');
INSERT INTO infosec_processed VALUES(452,'CVE-2026-11466','A weakness has been identified in zilliztech deep-searcher up to 0.0.2. This affects the function CollectionRouter.invoke of the file deepsearcher/agent/collection_router.py. This manipulation of the argument kwargs causes improper access controls. Remote exploitation of the attack is possible. The exploit has been made available to the public and could be used for attacks. The pull request to fix this issue awaits acceptance.','deep-searcher访问控制漏洞，可远程利用','漏洞',54,'zilliztech deep-searcher','NVD','2026-06-07T23:16:42.213',NULL,NULL,1781418236,'https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln/detail/CVE-2026-11466');
INSERT INTO infosec_processed VALUES(453,'CVE-2026-11467','A security vulnerability has been detected in jishenghua jshERP up to 3.6. This vulnerability affects the function addAccountHeadAndDetail of the file jshERP-boot/src/main/java/com/jsh/erp/service/AccountHeadService.java of the component addAccountHeadAndDetail Endpoint. Such manipulation of the argument fileName leads to path traversal. The attack can be executed remotely. The exploit has been disclosed publicly and may be used. The project was informed of the problem early through an issue report but has not responded yet.','jshERP系统存在路径遍历漏洞，可通过远程攻击利用','漏洞',54,'jshERP addAccountHeadAndDetail Endpoint','NVD','2026-06-08T00:16:42.230',NULL,NULL,1781418246,'https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln/detail/CVE-2026-11467');
INSERT INTO infosec_processed VALUES(454,'CVE-2026-11468','A vulnerability was detected in SourceCodester Hospitals Patient Records Management System 1.0. This issue affects some unknown processing of the file /admin/?page=room_types. Performing a manipulation of the argument room results in cross site scripting. The attack is possible to be carried out remotely. The exploit is now public and may be used.','医院患者记录管理系统存在XSS漏洞，可通过room参数触发','漏洞',24,'SourceCodester Hospitals Patient Records Management System 1.0','NVD','2026-06-08T00:16:42.387',NULL,NULL,1781418254,'https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln/detail/CVE-2026-11468');
INSERT INTO infosec_processed VALUES(455,'CVE-2026-11469','A flaw has been found in jishenghua jshERP up to 3.6. Impacted is the function insertPlatformConfig of the file jshERP-boot/src/main/java/com/jsh/erp/service/PlatformConfigService.java of the component platformConfig Add Endpoint. Executing a manipulation of the argument platformValue can lead to server-side request forgery. The attack may be performed from remote. The exploit has been published and may be used. The project was informed of the problem early through an issue report but has not responded yet.','jshERP平台配置组件存在服务器端请求伪造漏洞','漏洞',47,'platformConfig Add Endpoint','NVD','2026-06-08T00:16:42.580',NULL,NULL,1781418261,'https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln/detail/CVE-2026-11469');
INSERT INTO infosec_processed VALUES(456,'CVE-2026-11470','A vulnerability has been found in hs-web hsweb-framework up to 5.0.1. The affected element is the function denied of the file hsweb-system/hsweb-system-file/src/main/java/org/hswebframework/web/file/FileUploadProperties.java of the component File Upload. The manipulation of the argument filename leads to path traversal. It is possible to initiate the attack remotely. The exploit has been disclosed to the public and may be used. The identifier of the patch is 8009845b577d8a2c4bbf4fdd8e8913799a714be6. It is suggested to install a patch to address this issue.','hsweb-framework文件上传组件路径遍历漏洞','漏洞',63,'文件上传组件','NVD','2026-06-08T01:16:22.433',NULL,NULL,1781418267,'https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln/detail/CVE-2026-11470');
